flowchart TD
    Start([Test Execution]) --> Type{Test Type?}
    Type -- Unit --> RunUnit[Run Unit Tests]
    Type -- Integration --> RunInteg[Run Integration Tests]
    Type -- System --> RunSystem[Run System/E2E Tests]
    Type -- Performance --> RunPerf[Run Benchmarks]
    RunUnit --> UnitEnv[Setup Test Env]
    RunInteg --> IntegEnv[Setup DB + Network]
    RunSystem --> SystemEnv[Setup Full Stack]
    RunPerf --> PerfEnv[Setup Benchmark Env]
    UnitEnv --> ExecuteUnit[Execute Tests]
    IntegEnv --> ExecuteInteg[Execute Tests]
    SystemEnv --> ExecuteSystem[Execute Tests]
    PerfEnv --> ExecutePerf[Execute Benchmarks]
    ExecuteUnit --> CollectUnit[Collect Results]
    ExecuteInteg --> CollectInteg[Collect Results]
    ExecuteSystem --> CollectSystem[Collect Results]
    ExecutePerf --> CollectPerf[Collect Metrics]
    CollectUnit --> UnitPass{All Pass?}
    CollectInteg --> IntegPass{All Pass?}
    CollectSystem --> SystemPass{All Pass?}
    CollectPerf --> PerfPass{No Regression?}
    UnitPass -- Fail --> ReportFail[Report Failures]
    IntegPass -- Fail --> ReportFail
    SystemPass -- Fail --> ReportFail
    PerfPass -- Fail --> ReportRegress[Report Regression]
    ReportFail --> End([Tests Failed])
    ReportRegress --> End
    UnitPass -- Pass --> GenCoverage[Generate Coverage]
    IntegPass -- Pass --> GenCoverage
    SystemPass -- Pass --> GenCoverage
    GenCoverage --> CoverageOK{Coverage â‰¥ Threshold?}
    CoverageOK -- No --> ReportLowCov[Report Low Coverage]
    ReportLowCov --> End
    CoverageOK -- Yes --> PublishResults[Publish Test Results]
    PerfPass -- Pass --> PublishPerf[Publish Benchmarks]
    PublishPerf --> PublishResults
